# Voice & Audio Rules

- STT: Faster-Whisper large-v3-turbo (CUDA float16), latency < 300ms
- TTS: Kokoro (primary/fast), CSM (quality), XTTS v2 (cloning), latency first audio < 200ms
- VAD: Silero VAD v5 with adaptive noise floor
- Wake word: openWakeWord with custom ONNX model ("Hey Emily")
- End-to-end voice response target: < 2 seconds
- All audio processing is async
- Support for interruption handling and backchannel responses
- Owner voice verification via `users/owner_identity.py`
